Some weddings are grand.

Our journey has been anything but ordinary, but this weekend, it all came together. 💫 Five years, a few detours, and a whole lot of love later, we finally had our big celebration! We may have been “officially official” for a while, but this weekend felt like the real deal. 😉 Feeling so grateful for the love and blessings that filled the air. Eight years ago, a simple crush on my neighbor turned into a lifetime of love. Thank you to everyone who witnessed our vows and celebrated with us. 2.22.25 will forever be etched in our hearts.
